form-element.label: Maximum # of Instances
form-element.instructions: Specifies the maximum number of instances that can be started before resetting the Master/Slave pair. This value should not exceed the maximum number of node instances allowed by Appian (Default: 1000).
form-element.name: Field3

form-element.label: Email Recipients
form-element.instructions: Type the email addresses where the results will be sent.
form-element.name: Field4

form-element.label: Polling Frequency
form-element.instructions: How often to ask for the stats of the master/slave pair?
form-element.name: Field6

form-element.label: # of Master/Slave Process Pairs
form-element.instructions: Please indicate how many Master/Process pairs should run concurrently. These processes will be distributed across the exec engines, and the number of concurrently running process pairs will never exceed this value.
form-element.name: Field1
